&lt;h2 id=&#34;predict-the-block-hash&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#predict-the-block-hash&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Predict the block hash&lt;/h2&gt;
